name: Limbo Llama
description: Limbo Llama is the embodiment of the void. It’s almost as if he wasn’t there. But yet he’s always there. Waiting. Watching. Your indecision, there he is. Your hesitation, there he is. He stands in the middle, you could not tell if he was good or evil if you tried, and that’s scary itself. Does that make him human? Not in the slightest. He is Limbo Llama.
